# 🎨 **DRAWMASTER - NEW INITIAL SCREEN WITH GAME HISTORY & RULES**

## 🎯 **OVERVIEW**

Successfully implemented a new **initial screen layout** that displays **game history** and **visual game rules** when users first enter DrawMaster, similar to the provided image reference. This creates a more engaging and informative entry experience.

## ✅ **NEW FEATURES IMPLEMENTED**

