### **📊 Game History Panel**

#### **🎮 Last Game Information**
- ✅ **Score Display**: Shows last game score prominently
- ✅ **Date & Time**: Displays when the last game was played
- ✅ **Visual Highlight**: Golden background for importance
- ✅ **Real-time Updates**: Updates after each game completion

#### **📈 Statistics Tracking**
- ✅ **Total Games Played**: Complete game counter
- ✅ **Highest Score**: Personal best tracking
- ✅ **Average Score**: Calculated performance metric
- ✅ **Player Rank System**: Dynamic rank based on performance
  - 🏆 Cao thủ (200+ points)
  - 🥈 Chuyên gia (150+ points)
  - 🥉 Thành thạo (100+ points)
  - 📈 Tiến bộ (50+ points)
  - 🌟 Mới bắt đầu (< 50 points)

#### **🏆 Achievement System**
- ✅ **Dynamic Achievements**: Based on games played and scores
- ✅ **Motivational Messages**: Encouraging feedback
- ✅ **Progress Tracking**: Clear progression indicators

### **📖 Visual Game Rules Panel**

#### **🎯 Rule Illustration**
- ✅ **Circular Design**: Professional visual rule indicator
- ✅ **Symbol Prohibition**: Shows forbidden characters (A, 7, &, #)
- ✅ **Red Strike-through**: Clear visual prohibition indicator
- ✅ **Multiple Ring Design**: Aesthetic appeal with blue/orange rings

#### **ℹ️ Game Information**
- ✅ **Topic**: Tổng quát (General)
- ✅ **Target**: 70 điểm (70 points)
- ✅ **Language**: Tiếng Việt (Vietnamese)
- ✅ **Clear Rule Statement**: "Không vẽ chữ cái, số, và ký hiệu, ok?"

#### **🎨 Visual Design Elements**
- ✅ **Curved Banner Header**: Professional "LUẬT CHƠI" title
- ✅ **Gradient Graphics**: Modern visual appeal
- ✅ **Color-coded Information**: Easy to read layout
- ✅ **Confirmation Button**: Large, prominent "✓ XÁC NHẬN"

## 🛠️ **TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION**

### **💾 Data Persistence**
```csharp
// Settings.Designer.cs & Settings.settings
✅ LastGameScore: int (User-scoped setting)
✅ TotalGamesPlayed: int (Persistent counter)
✅ HighestScore: int (Personal best tracking)
✅ LastPlayedDate: DateTime (Game session tracking)
```

### **🔄 Game Flow Integration**
```csharp
✅ Login → Initial Screen → Waiting Room → Game → Results → Initial Screen
✅ Automatic history updates after game completion
✅ Real-time statistics calculation
✅ Dynamic achievement system
✅ Smooth UI transitions
```

### **🎨 Custom Graphics**
- ✅ **Hand-drawn Rule Circle**: Custom Paint event with GDI+
- ✅ **Curved Header Banner**: GraphicsPath with rounded corners
- ✅ **Gradient Backgrounds**: LinearGradientBrush effects
- ✅ **Avatar Animations**: Cute character illustrations

